d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=071b7370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=849315a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=d9e08dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=e92877a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下"},{"pid":"d709bbe0f988a500b0df8607d46a6b3a18b753aa","tid":2019071,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:46:23.000Z","msg":"之前中共都話：要將香港變full tibet<br />\n<br />\n即係香港人被逼同大陸人結婚<br />\n<br />\n深港關卡可能真係會拆"},{"pid":"be67c0835f5ac833d3ecb16b1defbf51e6de6ee4","tid":2019071,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11912cc0961e81b0beab066e6e2063f7effbbd32","tid":2019071,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"abcbc58c6ad20a3ce9857e176a707ceac0211251","tid":2019071,"uid":215876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:45:28.00